(32, 93, 'If there is something you want to know about, would you rather look it up in a book than talk to someone about it?'),
(33, 93, 'Do you get palpitations or thumping in your heart?'),
(34, 93, 'Do you like the kind of work that you need to pay close attention to?'),
(35, 93, 'Do you get attacks of shaking or trembling?'),
(36, 93, 'Would you always declare everything at customs, even if you knewyou could never be found out?'),
(37, 93, 'Do you hate being with a crowd who play jokes on one another?'),
(38, 93, 'Are you an irritable person?'),
(39, 93, 'Do you like doing things in which you have to act quickly?'),
(40, 93, 'Do you worry about awful things that might happen?'),
(41, 93, 'Are you slow and unhurried in the way you move?'),
