(43, 93, 'Do you have many nightmares?'),
(44, 93, 'Do you like talking to people so much that you never miss a chance of talking to a stranger?'),
(45, 93, 'Are you troubled by aches and pains?'),
(46, 93, 'Would you be very unhappy if you could not see lots of people most of the time?'),
(47, 93, 'Would you call yourself a nervous person?'),
(48, 93, 'Of all the people you know, are there some whom you definitely do not like?'),
(49, 93, 'Would you say that you were fairly self-confident?'),
(50, 93, 'Are you easily hurt when people find fault with you or your work?'),
(51, 93, 'Do you find it hard to really enjoy yourself at a lively party?'),
